('Stable Diffusion', 'stable-diffusion', 'https://logo.clearbit.com/stability.ai', 'https://stability.ai', 'Open-source AI image generation model that runs locally or in the cloud with full customization.', 'Stable Diffusion is a latent text-to-image diffusion model developed by Stability AI. As an open-source model, it can be run locally on consumer hardware or accessed via cloud APIs. It supports txt2img, img2img, inpainting, outpainting, and ControlNet workflows. The model has spawned a vast ecosystem of fine-tuned variants and community extensions.', 'c1000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002', 'free', 0.00, false, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '{"text_to_image": true, "img2img": true, "inpainting": true, "controlnet": true, "local_run": true, "api_access": true, "lora_support": true}', ARRAY['Completely free and open-source', 'Runs locally with no usage limits', 'Massive community and model ecosystem', 'Full control over generation parameters', 'No content restrictions when self-hosted'], ARRAY['Requires technical setup for local use', 'Hardware requirements can be demanding', 'No official managed UI out of the box', 'Quality varies by model checkpoint'], 8.8, 15000000, 2022, 'Stable Diffusion is the leading open-source AI image generator. Run locally for free or use cloud APIs. Supports ControlNet, LoRA, and thousands of community models.', '<h2>What is Stable Diffusion?</h2><p>Stable Diffusion is an open-source latent diffusion model released by Stability AI in 2022. Unlike commercial tools, it can be downloaded and run entirely on your own hardware, giving you unlimited generations with no per-image cost.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Stable Diffusion supports a wide range of workflows including text-to-image, image-to-image transformation, inpainting, and outpainting. The ControlNet extension adds pose and edge-guided generation. A massive library of community fine-tuned models (checkpoints) and LoRA adapters lets you generate nearly any art style.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The base model is completely free to download and use. Cloud-based interfaces like DreamStudio (by Stability AI) charge per-generation credits. Third-party UIs like AUTOMATIC1111 and ComfyUI are also free and open-source.</p>'),

('Adobe Firefly', 'adobe-firefly', 'https://logo.clearbit.com/adobe.com', 'https://firefly.adobe.com', 'Adobe''s generative AI image creation tool trained on licensed content for commercial-safe outputs.', 'Adobe Firefly is Adobe''s suite of generative AI models designed for creative professionals. Trained exclusively on Adobe Stock images, openly licensed content, and public domain works, Firefly outputs are safe for commercial use. It integrates directly into Photoshop, Illustrator, and Adobe Express, enabling Generative Fill, text effects, vector recoloring, and more.', 'c1000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002', 'freemium', 4.99, true, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '{"text_to_image": true, "generative_fill": true, "text_effects": true, "vector_recolor": true, "adobe_integration": true, "commercial_safe": true, "style_reference": true}', ARRAY['Commercially safe training data', 'Deep integration with Adobe Creative Cloud', 'High quality and photorealistic outputs', 'Generative Fill in Photoshop is industry-leading', 'Regular model updates included with subscription'], ARRAY['Requires Adobe subscription for full access', 'Limited free tier generative credits', 'Less stylistically diverse than open-source alternatives', 'Slower generation compared to some competitors'], 8.5, 20000000, 2023, 'Adobe Firefly is a commercially safe AI image generator integrated into Photoshop and Illustrator. Generate images, apply Generative Fill, and create text effects legally.', '<h2>What is Adobe Firefly?</h2><p>Adobe Firefly is Adobe''s flagship generative AI toolset launched in 2023. It is built into Adobe Creative Cloud applications and is specifically trained on licensed and public domain content, making its outputs safe for commercial projects without copyright concerns.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Firefly powers Generative Fill and Generative Expand in Photoshop, allowing seamless object removal and canvas extension. In Illustrator, it enables vector recoloring and generative shape creation. The standalone Firefly web app supports text-to-image generation with style references and structure controls.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Firefly is included in all paid Adobe Creative Cloud plans starting at $4.99/month for Adobe Express. Standalone Firefly subscriptions offer additional generative credits. A limited free tier is available without a Creative Cloud subscription.</p>'),

('Canva AI', 'canva-ai', 'https://logo.clearbit.com/canva.com', 'https://www.canva.com/ai-image-generator/', 'AI image generation built into Canva''s popular design platform for instant creative content.', 'Canva AI integrates multiple AI image generation capabilities directly into the Canva design platform used by over 170 million people. It includes Magic Media (text-to-image and text-to-video), Magic Edit (AI-powered photo editing), Background Remover, and Magic Eraser. Users can generate images and immediately use them in Canva templates for social media, presentations, and marketing materials.', 'c1000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002', 'freemium', 14.99, true, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '{"text_to_image": true, "magic_edit": true, "background_remover": true, "magic_eraser": true, "template_integration": true, "brand_kit": true, "text_to_video": true}', ARRAY['Seamlessly integrated into Canva design workflow', 'Huge library of templates to use generated images in', 'No design skills required', 'Supports team collaboration', 'Available on mobile apps'], ARRAY['Image generation quality below dedicated tools', 'Limited advanced controls for generation', 'Best features require Canva Pro subscription', 'Not suitable for standalone AI art creation'], 7.8, 80000000, 2013, 'Canva AI image generator creates images from text prompts inside Canva. Use Magic Media, Magic Edit, and Background Remover to enhance your designs instantly.', '<h2>What is Canva AI?</h2><p>Canva AI refers to the suite of artificial intelligence features embedded in Canva, the world''s most popular online design platform. The AI image generator, called Magic Media, lets users create images and videos from text prompts and immediately incorporate them into thousands of Canva templates.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Magic Media generates images in multiple styles including photorealistic, watercolor, anime, and more. Magic Edit lets you select any object in a photo and replace or modify it with a text prompt. Background Remover and Magic Eraser use AI to automate common photo editing tasks.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Canva Free includes limited Magic Media generations per month. Canva Pro at $14.99/month includes 500 AI generations per month along with the full suite of Magic features. Canva for Teams scales for larger organizations.</p>'),

('Leonardo AI', 'leonardo-ai', 'https://logo.clearbit.com/leonardo.ai', 'https://leonardo.ai', 'Professional AI image generation platform with fine-tuned models, ControlNet, and real-time canvas.', 'Leonardo AI is a professional-grade generative AI platform focused on game assets, concept art, and commercial creative work. It offers a library of fine-tuned models, a real-time canvas editor, ControlNet support, and the ability to train custom models. Leonardo is widely used in game development, product design, and marketing for its consistent style output and high image quality.', 'c1000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002', 'freemium', 12.00, true, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '{"fine_tuned_models": true, "controlnet": true, "real_time_canvas": true, "custom_model_training": true, "motion_generation": true, "api_access": true, "image_guidance": true}', ARRAY['High-quality outputs with fine-tuned models', 'Excellent for game assets and concept art', 'Real-time canvas for iterative creation', 'Generous free tier with 150 tokens/day', 'Custom model training available'], ARRAY['Can be complex for beginners', 'Token-based system can be confusing', 'Best models require paid subscription', 'Generation speed varies under high load'], 8.6, 12000000, 2022, 'Leonardo AI is a professional AI image generator for game art, concept design, and creative projects. Fine-tuned models, ControlNet, and a real-time canvas make it industry-leading.', '<h2>What is Leonardo AI?</h2><p>Leonardo AI is an advanced AI image generation platform designed for professional creatives, particularly in game development and digital art. It provides access to a curated library of fine-tuned Stable Diffusion models and proprietary models optimized for specific art styles and use cases.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Leonardo''s Real-Time Canvas allows artists to sketch and watch AI generate artwork simultaneously. The platform supports ControlNet for pose and structure guidance, motion generation for animating still i