('Jasper Art', 'jasper-art', 'https://logo.clearbit.com/jasper.ai', 'https://www.jasper.ai/art', 'AI image generator integrated into Jasper''s enterprise AI content platform for marketing teams.', 'Jasper Art is the AI image generation feature within Jasper, one of the leading enterprise AI content creation platforms. Designed for marketing teams and agencies, Jasper Art generates brand-consistent images from text prompts and integrates directly with Jasper''s document and campaign creation workflows. It is positioned for professional marketing use with brand voice and style consistency features.', 'c1000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002', 'paid', 49.00, true, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '{"marketing_focused": true, "brand_consistency": true, "jasper_integration": true, "team_collaboration": true, "unlimited_images": true, "multiple_styles": true, "api_access": true}', ARRAY['Unlimited image generation included in plans', 'Strong integration with Jasper writing workflow', 'Brand kit for consistent marketing imagery', 'Team collaboration features', 'Enterprise-grade reliability and support'], ARRAY['Expensive compared to dedicated image tools', 'Image quality not best-in-class', 'Requires Jasper subscription to access', 'Overkill for individual creators'], 7.5, 5000000, 2021, 'Jasper Art is an AI image generator for marketing teams, integrated into Jasper''s enterprise AI platform. Generate unlimited brand-consistent images with team collaboration features.', '<h2>What is Jasper Art?</h2><p>Jasper Art is the visual content generation module of Jasper, a leading enterprise AI content platform. It is designed specifically for marketing teams who need to produce consistent brand imagery at scale. Jasper Art is not a standalone product but rather an integral part of the Jasper content creation ecosystem.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Jasper Art generates images from text prompts in various styles suitable for marketing applications including blog headers, social media graphics, and ad creative. It integrates directly with Jasper''s document editor, allowing teams to generate images inline while writing content. Brand kit integration ensures generated imagery aligns with company visual guidelines.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Jasper Art is included in all Jasper paid plans starting at $49/month for the Creator plan. Teams plans start at $125/month for multiple seats. Jasper Art image generations are unlimited across all paid tiers, making it cost-effective for heavy marketing users within the Jasper ecosystem.</p>'),

('Stockimg.ai', 'stockimg-ai', 'https://logo.clearbit.com/stockimg.ai', 'https://stockimg.ai', 'AI image generator specialized in stock photos, logos, book covers, posters, and social media content.', 'Stockimg.ai is an AI image generation platform specifically designed for commercial content needs. It offers specialized generation modes for stock photos, logo design, book covers, poster creation, social media content, wallpapers, and illustrations. The platform aims to replace traditional stock photo subscriptions with AI-generated images tailored to specific commercial use cases.', 'c1000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002', 'freemium', 29.00, true, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '{"stock_photo_mode": true, "logo_generation": true, "book_cover": true, "poster_design": true, "social_media_templates": true, "wallpaper_generation": true, "illustration_mode": true}', ARRAY['Specialized modes for commercial content types', 'Good alternative to stock photo subscriptions', 'Logo and brand asset generation', 'Optimized for marketing and business use', 'Category-specific optimization improves quality'], ARRAY['Narrower creative scope than general tools', 'Higher starting price than competitors', 'Generation quality varies by category', 'Less suitable for artistic/creative expression'], 7.5, 1500000, 2023, 'Stockimg.ai generates commercial-ready AI images including stock photos, logos, book covers, and posters. Replace expensive stock photo subscriptions with unlimited AI-generated content.', '<h2>What is Stockimg.ai?</h2><p>Stockimg.ai is a specialized AI image generation platform built for commercial content creation. Rather than being a general-purpose image generator, it focuses on specific commercial use cases like stock photography, logo design, book covers, and marketing materials, with each mode optimized for its specific content type.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>The platform offers dedicated generation modes for stock photos, logos, book covers, posters, social media graphics, wallpapers, and illustrations. Each mode is fine-tuned for its specific content type, resulting in more commercially appropriate outputs than general-purpose generators. All generated content is licensed for commercial use.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Stockimg.ai offers a free trial with limited generations. Paid plans start at $29/month for the Starter plan. Pro at $79/month and Enterprise plans provide higher usage limits and additional features. The service positions itself as a cost-effective alternative to traditional stock photo subscriptions.</p>'),

('Krita AI', 'krita-ai', 'https://logo.clearbit.com/krita.org', 'https://krita.org', 'Free, open-source digital painting app with integrated AI image generation plugins for artists.', 'Krita is a professional, free, and open-source digital painting application that has gained AI capabilities through plugins, most notably the Krita AI Diffusion plugin. This plugin integrates Stable Diffusion directly into Krita''s painting environment, allowing artists to use AI for generating image compositions, filling selections with AI content, refining sketches, and extending canvases, all within a professional digital art workflow.', 'c1000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002', 'free', 0.00, false, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '{"open_source": true, "professional_painting_tools": true, "ai_diffusion_plugin": true, "local_generation": true, "inpainting": true, "sketch_refinement": true, "canvas_extension": true}', ARRAY['Completely free and open-source forever', 'Professional-grade painting tools for artists', 'AI generation integrated into painting workflow', 'Runs locally with no usage costs', 'Active development community'], ARRAY['Requires technical setup for AI features', 'Needs good GPU for local AI generation', 'AI plugin setup can be complex for beginners', 'Not a pure AI generator - primarily a painting app'], 8.2, 2000000, 2005, 'Krita is a free, open-source painting app with AI image generation via the Krita AI Diffusion plugin. Generate, inpaint, and extend images locally within a professional art workflow.', '<h2>What is Krita AI?</h2><p>Krita is a professional-grade open-source digital painting application originally focused on illustration and concept art. Through the Krita AI Diffusion plugin, artists can integrate Stable Diffusion AI generation directly into their painting workflow, using AI as a creative assistant rather than a standalone generator.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>The Krita AI Diffusion plugin enables text-to-image generation, inpainting within selections, sketch-to-image refinement, canvas outpainting, and real-time generation previews. All processing happens locally using the artist''s own GPU, ensuring complete privacy and no usage costs. The integration preserves Krita''s full layer and painting tool capabilities alongside AI features.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Krita is completely free and open-source with no subscription or usage fees. The AI Diffusion plugin is also free. The only cost is computing resources: a mid-range to high-end NVIDIA GPU is recommended for reasonable generation speeds. Cloud-based generation options are available through third-party services if local hardware is insufficient.</p>'),

('Imagen (Google)', 'imagen-google', 'https://logo.clearbit.com/google.com', 'https://imagen.research.google', 'Google''s state-of-the-art text-to-image diffusion model known for photorealism and prompt fidelity.', 'Imagen is Google''s family of text-to-image diffusion models developed by Google Research and Google DeepMind. Known for exceptional photorealism and strong prompt fidelity, Imagen and its successors (Imagen 2, Imagen 3) power image generation in Google products including Google Slides, Gmail, Workspace, and the Gemini AI assistant. Access for developers is available through Google Cloud Vertex AI.', 'c1000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002', 'paid', 0.02, true, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '{"photorealism": true, "prompt_fidelity": true, "google_workspace_integration": true, "vertex_ai_api": true, "imagen3_model": true, "inpainting": true, "outpainting": true}', ARRAY['Exceptional photorealism and image quality', 'Strong prompt understanding and adherence', 'Integrated into Google Workspace and Gemini', 'Enterprise-grade reliability via Vertex AI', 'Regular model improvements from Google Research'], ARRAY['Limited public access - primarily API/enterprise', 'Pricing can be high for large-scale use', 'Less accessible to individual creators', 'No dedicated consumer-facing web interface'], 8.7, 10000000, 2022, 'Google Imagen is a state-of-the-art text-to-image AI model known for photorealism and prompt accuracy. Access via Google Vertex AI API or through Google Workspace and Gemini products.', '<h2>What is Google Imagen?</h2><p>Imagen is Google''s family of advanced text-to-image AI models developed by Google Research and Google DeepMind. Starting with the original Imagen in 2022, Google has released increasingly capable versions culminating in Imagen 3, which represents one of the highest quality text-to-image models available as of 2026. The technology powers image generation across Google''s product suite.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Imagen models are renowned for exceptional photorealistic image quality and strong prompt fidelity - the ability to accurately render complex prompts with multiple subjects and specific attributes. The models power "Help me create an image" in Google Slides and Workspace, image generation in Gemini, and are available to developers through Google Cloud''s Vertex AI platform with full API access.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Consumer access to Imagen is available through Google Gemini (included in Google One AI Premium at $19.99/month) and Google Workspace AI features. Developer and enterprise access through Vertex AI is priced per image starting at approximately $0.02 per image, with volume discounts available for large-scale deployment.</p>'),

('Microsoft Designer', 'designer-microsoft', 'https://logo.clearbit.com/microsoft.com', 'https://designer.microsoft.com', 'Microsoft''s AI-powered design tool with DALL-E 3 image generation and template-based design creation.', 'Microsoft Designer is a free AI-powered design and image generation tool from Microsoft. Powered by DALL-E 3 for image generation and integrated with Microsoft''s design templates, it allows users to create social media posts, invitations, flyers, and other visual content. Designer is tightly integrated with Microsoft 365 and Copilot, making it part of Microsoft''s AI-powered productivity suite.', 'c1000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002', 'freemium', 6.99, true, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '{"dalle3_generation": true, "design_templates": true, "microsoft365_integration": true, "copilot_integration": true, "social_media_export": true, "brand_kit": true, "background_remover": true}', ARRAY['Free with Microsoft account', 'DALL-E 3 powered image generation', 'Beautiful pre-made templates', 'Deep Microsoft 365 integration', 'Easy to use for non-designers'], ARRAY['Limited advanced design control vs Canva', 'Requires Microsoft account', 'Stricter content filtering', 'Fewer templates than established design tools', 'Limited animation and video features'], 7.8, 15000000, 2022, 'Microsoft Designer is a free AI design tool powered by DALL-E 3. Create social media graphics, invitations, and marketing materials with AI image generation and design templates.', '<h2>What is Microsoft Designer?</h2><p>Microsoft Designer is a free AI-powered graphic design application launched by Microsoft in 2022. It combines DALL-E 3 image generation with a template-based design environment, allowing users to create professional-looking visual content without graphic design experience. It serves as Microsoft''s answer to Canva and is integrated throughout the Microsoft 365 ecosystem.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Designer generates images from text prompts using DALL-E 3 and suggests design layouts for various content types including social media posts, email headers, invitations, and presentations. Background removal, AI-powered image enhancement, and brand kit features allow for customized, consistent output. Integration with Copilot means designs can be created through conversational AI prompts.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Microsoft Designer is free for users with a Microsoft account, with daily generation limits. Microsoft 365 Personal and Family subscribers at $6.99/month receive additional generations and premium features. Microsoft 365 Business subscribers receive Designer as part of their plans. Copilot Pro subscribers get enhanced Designer capabilities.</p>'),

('PicsArt AI', 'picsart-ai', 'https://logo.clearbit.com/picsart.com', 'https://picsart.com/ai-image-generator/', 'AI image generation within PicsArt''s popular mobile and web photo editing and creative platform.', 'PicsArt is one of the world''s largest creative platforms with over 150 million monthly active users. Its AI capabilities include text-to-image generation, AI photo effects, background removal, object removal, AI avatars, and generative fill. The platform is particularly popular with Gen Z creators for social media content creation, combining powerful AI tools with an extensive sticker and template library.', 'c1000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002', 'freemium', 13.00, true, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '{"text_to_image": true, "ai_avatars": true, "generative_fill": true, "background_remover": true, "ai_effects": true, "sticker_library": true, "video_editing": true, "social_features": true}', ARRAY['Massive user base and community', 'Excellent mobile app experience', 'AI avatars very popular for profile pictures', 'Extensive sticker and template library', 'Good free tier for casual use'], ARRAY['Subscription required for best AI features', 'Image generation quality below dedicated tools', 'App can feel cluttered with features', 'Ads on free tier can be intrusive'], 7.5, 50000000, 2011, 'PicsArt AI image generator creates AI art and avatars within the world''s most popular creative platform. 150M monthly users use PicsArt for AI photos, effects, and social media content.', '<h2>What is PicsArt AI?</h2><p>PicsArt is a comprehensive creative platform with over 150 million monthly active users, making it one of the world''s largest creative communities. Its AI features, collectively marketed as PicsArt AI, encompass text-to-image generation, AI avatar creation, generative fill, background removal, and dozens of AI-powered photo effects and filters.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>PicsArt''s AI image generator creates images from text prompts in multiple artistic styles. The AI Avatar feature, which generates stylized profile pictures from selfies, became a viral sensation. Generative Fill allows AI-powered object replacement within photos. The platform''s strength lies in combining AI generation with an enormous library of stickers, fonts, templates, and a collaborative creator community.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>PicsArt offers a robust free tier with watermarked exports and limited AI credits. PicsArt Gold at $13/month removes watermarks, provides unlimited AI generations, and unlocks premium stickers and templates. PicsArt Teams plans are available for businesses and content agencies.</p>')

