('apify', 'apify', 'https://logo.clearbit.com/apify.com', 'https://apify.com', 'Web scraping and browser automation platform with a cloud-based actor marketplace.', 'Apify is a full-featured web scraping and automation platform that offers a marketplace of pre-built "Actors" (scrapers and automation scripts) as well as tools to build your own. Developers can use Apify''s SDK for Node.js or Python, while non-developers can use pre-built Actors from the marketplace. Apify handles proxies, anti-bot bypassing, scheduling, and result storage in the cloud.', 'c1000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000005', 'freemium', 0.00, true, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '{"actor_marketplace": true, "proxy_management": true, "anti_bot_bypass": true, "cloud_storage": true, "sdk_nodejs_python": true, "scheduling": true}', ARRAY['Large marketplace of pre-built scrapers', 'Handles proxies and anti-bot measures', 'Both no-code and developer-friendly', 'Generous free tier ($5/month credit)', 'Supports Node.js and Python SDKs'], ARRAY['Can be expensive at scale', 'Complex pricing model', 'Some Actors are community-maintained and may break', 'Steeper learning curve for custom Actors'], 8.4, 1500000, 2015, 'Apify is a web scraping platform with 1500+ pre-built Actors. Cloud-based automation with proxy management. Free $5/month credit included.', '<h2>What is Apify?</h2><p>Apify is a comprehensive web scraping and browser automation platform that caters to both developers and non-technical users. Its Actor marketplace contains 1,500+ pre-built scrapers and automation scripts for popular websites, allowing users to extract data without building from scratch.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Apify manages the complexity of web scraping infrastructure including proxy rotation, CAPTCHA handling, and anti-bot bypassing. The Apify SDK for Node.js and Python allows developers to build custom Actors. Results are stored in Apify''s cloud datasets and can be exported via API.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Apify provides $5 of free 