('phantombuster', 'phantombuster', 'https://logo.clearbit.com/phantombuster.com', 'https://phantombuster.com', 'Cloud-based automation tool for scraping and automating LinkedIn, Twitter, and other platforms.', 'PhantomBuster is a cloud-based automation platform specializing in lead generation and social media automation. It offers 100+ pre-built "Phantoms" and "Flows" for automating tasks on LinkedIn, Twitter/X, Instagram, GitHub, and more. Popular use cases include LinkedIn profile scraping, email finding, connection request automation, and data enrichment for sales teams.', 'c1000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000005', 'freemium', 0.00, true, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '{"linkedin_automation": true, "social_media_scraping": true, "email_finder": true, "100_plus_phantoms": true, "cloud_based": true, "lead_generation": true}', ARRAY['100+ pre-built automation templates', 'No coding required', 'Cloud-based, runs 24/7', 'Strong LinkedIn automation capabilities', 'Free trial available'], ARRAY['Risk of account bans on LinkedIn', 'Free tier very limited (2 hours/month)', 'Some Phantoms can be unreliable', 'Not suitable for large-scale enterprise use'], 7.4, 900000, 2016, 'PhantomBuster automates LinkedIn, Twitter, and social media for lead generation. 100+ pre-built Phantoms. Cloud-based with no coding required.', '<h2>What is PhantomBuster?</h2><p>PhantomBuster is a cloud-based automation tool designed for growth hackers, sales teams, and marketers who need to automate lead generation and social media tasks. With 100+ pre-built Phantoms, you can automate LinkedIn outreach, scrape profiles, find email addresses, and enrich CRM data without writing code.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>PhantomBuster''s Phantom library covers LinkedIn, Twitter/X, Instagram, GitHub, Google, and more. Flows combine multiple Phantoms into end-to-end lead generation pipelines. All automation runs in the cloud, so your computer doesn''t need to be on.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The free plan includes 2 hours of 