('clay-hq', 'clay-hq', 'https://logo.clearbit.com/clay.com', 'https://www.clay.com', 'AI-powered data enrichment and outreach automation platform for sales teams.', 'Clay is an AI-powered data enrichment and sales automation platform that pulls data from 75+ sources to build hyper-personalized outreach campaigns. Sales teams use Clay to enrich lead lists with company data, contact information, and buying signals, then use AI to write personalized email copy at scale. Clay is widely considered the most powerful tool in the modern sales tech stack for outbound-focused teams.', 'c1000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000005', 'freemium', 0.00, true, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '{"75_plus_data_sources": true, "ai_email_writing": true, "waterfall_enrichment": true, "crm_sync": true, "lead_research": true, "outreach_automation": true}', ARRAY['75+ data enrichment sources', 'AI-powered personalized email writing', 'Waterfall enrichment for maximum data coverage', 'Powerful for outbound sales teams', 'Integrates with major CRMs and email tools'], ARRAY['Steep learning curve', 'Can be expensive at scale', 'Credit-based pricing is complex', 'Best suited for technical sales teams'], 8.7, 700000, 2021, 'Clay is an AI sales platform with 75+ data sources for lead enrichment and personalized outreach. The top tool for modern outbound sales teams.', '<h2>What is Clay?</h2><p>Clay is an AI-powered data enrichment and outreach automation platform that has become the go-to tool for modern outbound sales teams. It aggregates data from 75+ sources including LinkedIn, Apollo, Clearbit, and more to build comprehensive lead profiles, then uses AI to write highly personalized email copy at scale.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Clay''s "waterfall enrichment" tries multiple data providers in sequence to maximize data coverage. The AI researcher can browse the web and summarize information about prospects. Claygent (AI agent) can perform custom research tasks on each lead automatically.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>