('lemlist', 'lemlist', 'https://logo.clearbit.com/lemlist.com', 'https://lemlist.com', 'AI-powered cold email and multichannel outreach platform with personalization.', 'Lemlist is an AI-powered cold email and multichannel outreach platform that specializes in personalized email campaigns at scale. It features dynamic image and video personalization, email warm-up technology, LinkedIn automation, and AI-assisted email writing. Lemlist is popular among sales development reps and agencies for its ability to create highly personalized cold outreach campaigns.', 'c1000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000005', 'paid', 39.00, true, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '{"email_personalization": true, "image_video_personalization": true, "email_warmup": true, "linkedin_automation": true, "ai_email_writing": true, "multichannel_sequences": true}', ARRAY['Dynamic image and video personalization', 'Built-in email warm-up tool', 'Multichannel (email + LinkedIn) sequences', 'AI email writing assistance', 'Strong deliverability focus'], ARRAY['Higher price point than competitors', 'LinkedIn automation has ToS risks', 'Interface can be complex for beginners', 'Warm-up tool requires separate subscription'], 7.8, 800000, 2018, 'Lemlist is an AI cold email platform with image/video personalization and email warm-up. Multichannel outreach for sales teams from $39/month.', '<h2>What is Lemlist?</h2><p>Lemlist is an AI-powered cold email and multichannel outreach platform known for its innovative personalization features. Sales teams can create campaigns with dynamically personalized images and videos for each prospect, significantly improving reply rates compared to generic outreach.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Lemlist''s email warm-up tool (lemwarm) helps new email accounts build sender reputation. Multichannel sequences combine email, LinkedIn messages, and calls. The AI writing assistant generates personalized email copy based on prospect data.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Plans start at $39/month per seat for