('instantly-ai', 'instantly-ai', 'https://logo.clearbit.com/instantly.ai', 'https://instantly.ai', 'Cold email outreach platform with unlimited email sending accounts and AI personalization.', 'Instantly.ai is a cold email platform that stands out by offering unlimited email sending accounts on all plans, making it ideal for agencies and high-volume senders. It features built-in email warm-up for all connected accounts, AI-powered email writing, A/B testing, and a comprehensive analytics dashboard. Instantly is designed to maximize cold email deliverability and scale outreach without the per-seat costs of competitors.', 'c1000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000005', 'paid', 37.00, true, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '{"unlimited_sending_accounts": true, "built_in_warmup": true, "ai_email_writing": true, "ab_testing": true, "deliverability_analytics": true, "lead_database": true}', ARRAY['Unlimited sending accounts on all plans', 'Built-in email warm-up included', 'Excellent deliverability features', 'AI personalization at scale', 'Affordable for high-volume senders'], ARRAY['Limited multichannel (email focused)', 'Lead database quality can vary', 'CRM features are basic', 'No native LinkedIn automation'], 8.3, 1100000, 2021, 'Instantly.ai offers unlimited cold email accounts with built-in warm-up and AI personalization. Best for high-volume outreach from $37/month.', '<h2>What is Instantly?</h2><p>Instantly.ai is a cold email outreach platform designed for scale. Its defining feature is unlimited email sending accounts on all paid plans, making it the preferred choice for agencies managing multiple client campaigns and high-volume outbound sales teams.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Every Instantly plan includes built-in email warm-up for all connected accounts. The AI writing assistant personalizes emails at scale. Comprehensive analytics track deliverability, open rates, reply rates, and campaign performance. The built-in lead database allows prospecting within the platform.</p><h