('apollo-io', 'apollo-io', 'https://logo.clearbit.com/apollo.io', 'https://www.apollo.io', 'All-in-one sales intelligence platform with a 270M+ contact database and engagement tools.', 'Apollo.io is a comprehensive sales intelligence and engagement platform that combines a massive B2B contact database (270M+ contacts, 60M+ companies) with outreach automation tools. Sales teams use Apollo to find prospects, enrich data, send cold emails, and track engagement all in one platform. Apollo''s AI features help with email writing, prospect scoring, and conversation intelligence.', 'c1000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000005', 'freemium', 0.00, true, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '{"270m_contact_database": true, "email_outreach": true, "crm_integration": true, "ai_email_writing": true, "intent_data": true, "linkedin_extension": true}', ARRAY['270M+ contact database', 'Free plan with generous limits', 'All-in-one prospecting and outreach', 'Strong CRM integrations', 'LinkedIn Chrome extension'], ARRAY['Data accuracy can be inconsistent', 'UI can feel overwhelming', 'Email deliverability issues reported', 'Customer support can be slow'], 8.1, 8000000, 2015, 'Apollo.io has a 270M+ contact database with cold email and sales automation. Free plan available. All-in-one sales intelligence platform.', '<h2>What is Apollo.io?</h2><p>Apollo.io is one of the most popular all-in-one sales intelligence platforms, combining a database of 270M+ contacts and 60M+ companies with built-in email outreach, sequencing, and CRM integration. It''s used by over 160,000 companies ranging from startups to enterprises.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Apollo''s contact database allows filtering by job title, company size, industry, technology stack, and more. The LinkedIn Chrome extension enriches profiles with contact data. AI-powered email writing and scoring help prioritize and personalize outreach. Intent data signals help identify companies actively researching solutions.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Apollo offers a free plan with 10 email credits/month. The Basic plan starts at $49/month per user with 900 email credits. Professional and Organization plans offer more credits, features, and team capabilities.</p>'),

('smartlead-ai', 'smartlead-ai', 'https://logo.clearbit.com/smartlead.ai', 'https://www.smartlead.ai', 'AI-powered cold email platform with unlimited mailboxes and advanced deliverability features.', 'Smartlead is an AI-powered cold email outreach platform focused on deliverability and scale. Like Instantly, it offers unlimited mailboxes on all plans. Its AI features include smart email rotation, warmup automation, and AI-personalized email sequences. Smartlead is particularly popular among agencies for its white-labeling capabilities and client management features.', 'c1000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000005', 'paid', 39.00, true, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '{"unlimited_mailboxes": true, "ai_warmup": true, "white_label": true, "smart_rotation": true, "multichannel": true, "client_management": true}', ARRAY['Unlimited mailboxes on all plans', 'White-label option for agencies', 'AI-powered email warm-up', 'Smart mailbox rotation for deliverability', 'Client management dashboard'], ARRAY['Newer platform with less market presence', 'Some features still in development', 'Documentation could be better', 'Limited integrations compared to mature platforms'], 7.7, 400000, 2022, 'Smartlead.ai offers unlimited mailboxes with AI warm-up and white-labeling for agencies. Advanced cold email deliverability from $39/month.', '<h2>What is Smartlead?</h2><p>Smartlead.ai is an AI-powered cold email platform built with agencies and high-volume senders in mind. Its unlimited mailbox model means you can connect as many email accounts as needed without extra costs, while AI-powered warm-up maintains sender reputation across all accounts.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Smartlead''s smart rotation distributes email sending across mailboxes to maximize deliverability. The white-label feature lets agencies brand the platform for their clients. The master inbox consolidates replies from all campaigns in one place. AI writing assistance personalizes emails at scale.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The Basic plan starts at $39/month with unlimited mailboxes and 2,000 active leads. The Pro plan at $94/month adds more leads and advanced features. A 14-day free trial is available for all plans.</p>'),

('gong-io', 'gong-io', 'https://logo.clearbit.com/gong.io', 'https://www.gong.io', 'AI-powered revenue intelligence platform for recording, analyzing, and coaching sales calls.', 'Gong is the leading AI-powered revenue intelligence platform that records and analyzes sales calls, emails, and meetings to provide actionable insights. It uses AI to identify winning behaviors, flag deal risks, coach reps, and forecast revenue. Gong is used by thousands of sales organizations to understand what separates top performers from the rest and replicate successful patterns across the team.', 'c1000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000005', 'enterprise', 16000.00, false, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '{"call_recording": true, "ai_analysis": true, "deal_intelligence": true, "coaching_tools": true, "revenue_forecasting": true, "crm_integration": true}', ARRAY['Industry-leading AI call analysis', 'Deep CRM integration', 'Powerful coaching and onboarding features', 'Accurate revenue forecasting', 'Identifies winning sales behaviors at scale'], ARRAY['Very expensive (typically $1,200-1,600 per user/year)', 'Minimum contract requirements', 'Complex implementation process', 'Overkill for small sales teams'], 8.8, 1200000, 2015, 'Gong.io is the leading revenue intelligence platform. AI analyzes sales calls to improve win rates, coach reps, and forecast revenue.', '<h2>What is Gong?</h2><p>Gong is the market-leading revenue intelligence platform that uses AI to capture and analyze every customer interaction—calls, emails, and meetings. It surfaces insights that help sales leaders understand what''s working, coach reps more effectively, and forecast revenue with greater accuracy.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Gong''s AI automatically transcribes and analyzes sales calls, identifying topics, competitor mentions, and deal risks. Deal intelligence tracks engagement levels and predicts likelihood to close. Coaching tools allow managers to leave timestamped comments on call recordings and create playlists of winning moments.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Gong uses custom enterprise pricing, typically ranging from $1,200 to $1,600 per user per year plus a platform fee. Minimum contracts are usually required. Contact sales for a custom quote.</p>'),

('chorus-ai', 'chorus-ai', 'https://logo.clearbit.com/chorus.ai', 'https://www.chorus.ai', 'Conversation intelligence platform by ZoomInfo for analyzing sales calls and meetings.', 'Chorus.ai, now part of ZoomInfo, is a conversation intelligence platform that records, transcribes, and analyzes sales calls and meetings. It integrates deeply with the ZoomInfo data platform, providing context about prospects during call analysis. Chorus uses AI to identify key moments, track competitors, and score calls against customizable criteria. It''s a strong Gong alternative, especially for teams already using ZoomInfo.', 'c1000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000005', 'enterprise', 15000.00, false, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '{"call_recording": true, "ai_transcription": true, "zoominfo_integration": true, "deal_intelligence": true, "coaching_scorecards": true, "competitor_tracking": true}', ARRAY['Deep ZoomInfo data integration', 'AI-powered call scoring and coaching', 'Competitor mention tracking', 'Strong CRM integrations', 'Good meeting intelligence features'], ARRAY['Requires ZoomInfo ecosystem for best value', 'Less innovative than Gong', 'Expensive enterprise pricing', 'Some users report accuracy issues with transcription'], 7.9, 600000, 2015, 'Chorus.ai by ZoomInfo is a conversation intelligence platform for analyzing sales calls. AI coaching, deal insights, and CRM integration.', '<h2>What is Chorus.ai?</h2><p>Chorus.ai, acquired by ZoomInfo in 2021, is a conversation intelligence platform that records and analyzes sales calls, video meetings, and email threads. As part of the ZoomInfo ecosystem, Chorus combines contact intelligence data with conversation analysis for a more complete picture of each deal.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Chorus AI transcribes calls and identifies key moments like next steps, competitor mentions, and pricing discussions. Coaching scorecards let managers evaluate rep performance against defined criteria. The ZoomInfo integration enriches call analysis with real-time prospect data.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Chorus.ai uses custom enterprise pricing, typically bundled with ZoomInfo subscriptions. Contact ZoomInfo sales for pricing. A demo is available upon request.</p>'),

('exceed-ai', 'exceed-ai', 'https://logo.clearbit.com/exceed.ai', 'https://exceed.ai', 'AI sales assistant that automates lead qualification and follow-up via email and chat.', 'Exceed.ai is an AI-powered sales assistant platform that automates lead engagement, qualification, and meeting scheduling through conversational email and chat. The AI assistant has two-way conversations with leads, qualifies them based on defined criteria, and books meetings with sales reps when leads are ready. Exceed is now part of Genesys and is used by enterprise sales teams to handle top-of-funnel qualification at scale.', 'c1000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000005', 'enterprise', 2000.00, true, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '{"ai_sales_assistant": true, "automated_qualification": true, "meeting_scheduling": true, "conversational_email": true, "crm_integration": true, "multilingual": true}', ARRAY['Automates repetitive lead qualification', 'Two-way conversational AI', 'Seamless handoff to human reps', 'Reduces SDR workload significantly', 'CRM integration keeps data in sync'], ARRAY['Enterprise pricing', 'AI conversations can feel robotic', 'Setup and training requires time investment', 'Limited customization on lower tiers'], 7.3, 150000, 2016, 'Exceed.ai automates lead qualification and follow-up with conversational AI. Books meetings for sales reps 24/7 via email and chat.', '<h2>What is Exceed.ai?</h2><p>Exceed.ai is an AI-powered virtual sales assistant that automates the top of the sales funnel. The AI engages inbound and outbound leads via email and chat, asks qualifying questions, and books meetings with human sales reps when a lead meets your qualification criteria—all without human intervention.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Exceed''s AI handles objections, answers FAQs, and maintains natural-sounding two-way email conversations. It integrates with major CRMs to keep lead data synchronized. Multilingual support allows engagement with leads in their native language. Now part of the Genesys platform.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Exceed.ai uses custom enterprise pricing starting around $2,000/month depending on volume and features. Contact sales for a custom quote. A demo is available.</p>'),

('salesloft', 'salesloft', 'https://logo.clearbit.com/salesloft.com', 'https://salesloft.com', 'AI-powered sales engagement platform for managing the full revenue lifecycle.', 'Salesloft is a leading AI-powered sales engagement platform that helps revenue teams manage cadences, analyze conversations, forecast deals, and coach reps—all in one platform. After acquiring Drift (conversational AI) and Drift''s buyer engagement tools, Salesloft now covers the entire revenue lifecycle. It competes directly with Outreach.io and is used by enterprise sales teams globally.', 'c1000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000005', 'enterprise', 12500.00, false, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '{"sales_cadences": true, "conversation_intelligence": true, "deal_management": true, "revenue_forecasting": true, "coaching": true, "drift_integration": true}', ARRAY['End-to-end revenue lifecycle management', 'Strong cadence and sequencing features', 'Integrated conversation intelligence', 'Accurate AI forecasting', 'Enterprise-grade security and compliance'], ARRAY['Very expensive for small teams', 'Steep learning curve', 'Some features overlap with CRM', 'Requires dedicated admin'], 8.2, 900000, 2011, 'Salesloft is an AI sales engagement platform covering cadences, conversation intelligence, and revenue forecasting. Enterprise solution for modern sales teams.', '<h2>What is Salesloft?</h2><p>Salesloft is a leading AI-powered sales engagement platform that helps revenue teams execute their go-to-market strategy. It provides tools for sales cadences, email and call tracking, conversation intelligence, deal management, and revenue forecasting in a unified platform.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Salesloft''s Cadence feature automates multi-step outreach sequences across email, phone, and LinkedIn. Conversation intelligence (formerly Drift) analyzes calls and meetings for coaching insights. AI-powered forecasting helps revenue leaders predict quarterly performance with greater accuracy.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Salesloft uses custom enterprise pricing typically starting around $125 per user per month with minimum seat requirements. Annual contracts are standard. Contact sales for a custom quote.</p>')

